{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "01b - Test Verification",
  "description": "Runs all tests (RunTests.ps1) after task completion and BEFORE build. Acts as a quality gate.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileCreated",
    "patterns": [
      ".kiro/specs/**/.tasks-complete"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "🧪 TEST VERIFICATION HOOK ACTIVATED\n\nTrigger: .tasks-complete marker detected (after task completion, before build)\nFile: $EDITED_FILE\n\n## YOUR MISSION:\nRun the full test suite to ensure code quality before allowing the build to proceed.\n\n---\n\n## STEP 1: RUN TESTS\n\nExecute the unified test script:\n\n```powershell\n& \"D:\\KSmartBiz\\KarmaTech_AI_EDR\\RunTests.ps1\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## STEP 2: HANDLE RESULTS\n\n**If Tests PASS (Exit Code 0):**\n- Report success\n- Create a marker to allow the next hook (Build) to proceed (if Build hook was waiting for this, but currently Build hook watches .tasks-complete too. We need to update Build hook to watch .tests-passed instead? Or just let this hook run independently and stop if it fails?)\n- Actually, better design: This hook runs *instead* of going straight to build? No, hooks run in parallel or sequence based on triggers.\n- **Current Design Adjustment**: The `02-build-publish` hook watches `.tasks-complete`. We should probably change `02-build-publish` to watch `.tests-passed` to enforce the gate.\n\n**Action for this hook:**\n1. Run tests\n2. If pass:\n   ```bash\n   echo \"tests-passed\" > .kiro/specs/[feature-name]/.tests-passed\n   git add .\n   git commit -m \"test: all tests passed for [feature-name]\"\n   git push origin feature/[feature-name]\n   ```\n3. If fail:\n   - Report error\n   - STOP. Do not create .tests-passed marker.\n\n---\n\n## OUTPUT FORMAT:\n\nSuccess:\n```\n📋 Feature: [feature-name]\n🧪 Running RunTests.ps1...\n✅ All Tests: PASSED\n📄 Created .tests-passed marker\n🔔 Hook 02 (Build & Publish) will trigger next (once configured to watch this marker)\n```\n\nFailure:\n```\n📋 Feature: [feature-name]\n🧪 Running RunTests.ps1...\n❌ Tests FAILED\n🛑 Stopping deployment - fix tests first\n```"
  },
  "workspaceFolderName": "KarmaTech_AI_EDR",
  "shortName": "01-b-test-verification"
}